cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.DS

This paper deals with the problem of multipath routing in wireless sensor networks for multimedia applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the optimization of network lifetime, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also addresses interference and energy-saving, which are topics covered in cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper uses simulations to evaluate the proposed approach, which falls under the category of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
